Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.64,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:20.18,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.80,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.55,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.36,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.50,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.50,0:01:22.85,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:27.58,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:34.52,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You know already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the elm tree where Rei waited for you yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She got soaked and caught a fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you care at all what happens to Rei!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It is of no concern to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rei is your younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}13. A Tale of Double Suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to waste my time listening to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:13.37,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Rei...\N 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Rei send you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:13.88,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain she would never ask you to speak to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless... you're an outsider, and must stay out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite your friendship and despite your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Her sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste is Miya-sama's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No way... Can it be true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Chigusa-Cho... 1-17-15 Maison d'Eduard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:03:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Room 507.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,An icy room filled with mirrors...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...a light in the kitchen that doesn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...that's Saint-Juste's... that's her room...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's her lonely room... her lonely little world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother... the sandwich I left for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That sandwich remains untouched at her door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So... are you in your room right now? Or out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My phone calls are all that can penetrate your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't enter your world myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only hope that you will open your door of your own free will...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...smiling, and saying "Hi"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...emerging from your deep, dark, mysterious world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,From your private world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard today that you are Miya-sama's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you have different last names.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this be? And what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But, those things aside, are you eating well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I worry about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But Rei is your younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you all over, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you doing out with a fever like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me... please... did you visit the elm tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She was waiting for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you tell her why I wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you explain it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop your nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you be reasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... hello? Yes, Asaka....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you? How do you feel? Did you eat something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Some soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fixing some for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness! You're there with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved! Saint-Juste isn't alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sleeping right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still got a bit of fever, but it's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming over now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know what time it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's well past the time for freshmen to be out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get to the convenience store... and brings lots of good food...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't. I'll hang up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... what kind of food... does Saint-Juste like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it... I don't remember ever seeing her enjoy eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow it. Not with your fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could only wash it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...I want to wash all of it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here... here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How about coffee? I'll make some.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you do that, maybe you should help me get her dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste remained asleep the entire time I was there in her room with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch a cab at the main street.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you'll be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.42,0:12:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't go to school after getting no sleep all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. I'm good at handling hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We can only wait for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When she finally gives up fighting this thing alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...that's when she'll come to us for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So that she can get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So that she can finally get over this agony and start to live again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting this out is a test of my friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But she can be very trying...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing which connects them both so closely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...is this what true friendship is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If that is how real friendship works, it's so different from me and Tomoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We are much more selfish about our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We think of friendship as something which entitles,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...not as something which obligates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They are only a year older than us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...yet they are so much more kind to each other, so much more patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to understand why and how that could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:14:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless it is something more special than mere friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless this is a deeper bond based on some kind of doomed emotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... the sun is shining, everything is lush and green!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a heaven of dancing birds, glistening water, and singing flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...all telling me to be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But despite all this loveliness, a doom awaits us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A terrible doom! Also known as "mid-terms"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You should eat something before afternoon classes start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks... I'm too depressed to have an appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...but-but-but!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But eating is my way of fighting back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it helps me keep a positive attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I envy all you Sorority members!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are different from us... you look so confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm not confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about your cram sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Sorority sisters are telling you what's covered on the tests!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but not all that's covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Nanako, you're my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can prove your friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Prove me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Loan me your cram school notes! I'll make a copy and return them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Please? Mariko, you too, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It was early afternoon after lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:16:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...that was when the strange rumors began.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one was that piano music was heard in the music hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...but there was no one inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one was that during 4th period,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...footsteps were heard in the empty north building,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...going up and down, up and down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there was the third rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It gave me a bit of a chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That there was a sound from the elm tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...a deep, soulful, sad sobbing... ...carried aloft by the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...which was heard from as far away as the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Those substances which oxidize other materials are called oxidants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,While oxidizing other materials, oxidants themselves are reduced during the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san, you're so naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We always hear these sorts of rumors just before exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Before exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... everyone gets so terribly stressed and nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So they start mixing up fact and fiction like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm... I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you could say it is a tradition here at Seiran...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The rumors before last year's exams were even scarier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The story is that someone was seen at the piano in the music hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The scary thing was that there were actually two of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One was a splendid woman in men's attire, a white tuxedo;
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The other was a female student in a hakama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Every afternoon they were seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...climbing the stairs of the north building, up and down,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the fading light of the sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They were said to be Seiran seniors from the beginning of the {\i1}Showa{\i0} era.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And they were doomed lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, they cut their wrists with a razor,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...together, under the elm tree, in the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, those two always reappear at exam time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think it's a deliciously romantic story...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... that elm tree, in the courtyard... it has such a history!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did they have to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But it must have made them happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...being able to die with someone they loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Hey! Are you implying something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Nanako-san, let's go to the Sorority house!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our cram session is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, off I go. See you tomorrow, Tomoko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... um... oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck! Don't forget the notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You were up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well! Study hard, then, at your cram session.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming from the music hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on ahead to the Sorority house, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it! That melody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited. Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Under that elm tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you've had a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Very bad. Your fever is still high.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to go home. To your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest yourself there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Be here! Saint-Juste-sama, you have to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.47,0:23:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama! Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.59,0:23:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time... all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.88,0:23:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you would someday keep your promise to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not her!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as you told me then...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...you've come here so we can... die together...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.70,0:23:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...you said... we could die together...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.71,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's mad! She's gone completely mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:14.21,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:19.68,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.15,0:24:25.29,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.29,0:24:30.76,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.50,0:24:37.04,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.04,0:24:42.51,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:45.24,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.24,0:24:48.05,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.05,0:24:50.45,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.45,0:24:55.72,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.72,0:25:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei embraces Nanako, insisting that they die together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.19,0:25:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Though she struggles to escape from the deranged Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.98,0:25:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...Nanako ends up cornered against the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.78,0:25:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei draws her knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.41,0:25:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the madness which flashes in her eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.16,0:25:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: The Secret Door
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.32,0:25:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
